---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import LeadMagnetForm from '../components/LeadMagnetForm.jsx';
---

<Layout
  title="Get Found on Google - Free Setup Guide | YourHQ"
  description="A free step-by-step guide to setting up your Google Business Profile. No jargon. No homework. Just the steps. For NZ small businesses."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-paper min-h-screen">

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 border-b border-carbon bg-[size:40px_40px] bg-grid-pattern relative">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">

        <div class="inline-block bg-frangipani/20 border border-frangipani px-4 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full">
            <span class="font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-carbon">Free Guide</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-8">
          Get Found on Google<br />
          <span class="text-gray-400 text-3xl md:text-5xl block mt-2 font-bold tracking-tight">The No-Nonsense Setup Guide</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-carbon/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Half of NZ businesses still don't have a proper Google presence. Not because they don't want one ‚Äî because every guide makes it sound harder than it is. This one's different.
        </p>

        <a href="#get-the-guide" class="inline-block bg-signal text-white px-10 py-4 border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard hover:shadow-none hover:translate-y-[2px] transition-all font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-lg">
            Get the Free Guide ‚Üí
        </a>

        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4 font-mono">Takes 20 minutes. You'll need your phone and a coffee. That's it.</p>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE PROBLEM (Dark) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-white">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-frangipani">You're Invisible to New Customers.</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl font-light leading-relaxed text-gray-200">
                <p>When someone Googles "plumber near me" or "best caf√© in [your town]" ‚Äî do you show up?</p>
                <p class="font-bold text-white">If you don't have a Google Business Profile, the answer is no. And that's work walking straight to your competitor.</p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/20 mt-8">
                    <p>The good news? Setting it up is free, takes about 20 minutes, and this guide walks you through every step.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHAT'S INSIDE -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

                <!-- Left: The "Book" Visual -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-paper border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard p-8 flex flex-col justify-center text-center">
                        <span class="text-6xl mb-4">üìç</span>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-2">Get Found<br/>on Google</h3>
                        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase mt-2">YourHQ Setup Guide</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Decorative elements -->
                    <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-signal/10 rounded-full blur-xl -z-10"></div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-hibiscus/10 rounded-full blur-xl -z-10"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right: The List -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-8">What you'll get:</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-6">
                        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-signal text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">‚úì</div>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Step-by-step setup instructions</strong> that actually make sense</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-signal text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">‚úì</div>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Category recommendations</strong> for tradies, salons, and service businesses</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-signal text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">‚úì</div>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Verification tips</strong> so you don't get stuck at the tricky part</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-signal text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">‚úì</div>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>What to do once you're live</strong> ‚Äî the maintenance is lighter than you think</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-signal text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">‚úì</div>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Photo and description tips</strong> that make your listing stand out</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHO THIS IS FOR -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-carbon p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">This guide is for you if...</h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-6">
                    <p class="flex gap-3 text-carbon font-medium">
                        <span class="text-hibiscus font-bold">‚Üí</span>
                        You don't show up when people Google your business name
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex gap-3 text-carbon font-medium">
                        <span class="text-hibiscus font-bold">‚Üí</span>
                        You've been meaning to "do the Google thing" but haven't got round to it
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex gap-3 text-carbon font-medium">
                        <span class="text-hibiscus font-bold">‚Üí</span>
                        You tried setting it up once and got stuck on verification
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex gap-3 text-carbon font-medium">
                        <span class="text-hibiscus font-bold">‚Üí</span>
                        Your competitors show up on Google Maps and you don't
                    </p>
                    <p class="flex gap-3 text-carbon font-medium md:col-span-2">
                        <span class="text-hibiscus font-bold">‚Üí</span>
                        You want new customers to find you without relying 100% on word-of-mouth
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SOCIAL PROOF -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-paper border-2 border-carbon p-8">
                    <p class="text-carbon text-lg italic mb-4">"This is exactly what I needed. Clear, simple, and it actually worked. Now I show up when people Google my name."</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-sm text-gray-500">‚Äî Sarah, Wellness Practitioner</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-paper border-2 border-carbon p-8">
                    <p class="text-carbon text-lg italic mb-4">"I'd been putting this off for months. Took me 15 minutes with the guide. Should've done it ages ago."</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-sm text-gray-500">‚Äî Mike, Electrician</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FORM SECTION -->
    <section id="get-the-guide" class="py-24 bg-paper">
        <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-4">

            <div class="text-center mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-4">Get Your Free Copy</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Enter your details and we'll email you the PDF.</p>
            </div>

            <LeadMagnetForm client:load source="google-guide" buttonText="Send Me The Guide" pdfUrl="/get-found-google-maps-tradie-guide.pdf" />

            <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
            <div class="mt-16 text-center border-t border-gray-200 pt-12">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-lg mx-auto">
                    This guide is brought to you by <strong>YourHQ</strong> ‚Äî founder-led websites for Kiwi small businesses. Built in 5 days, no homework, and looked after long-term. Need more than just a Google listing? <a href="/" class="text-signal underline">See what we do</a>.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
